lenders.name: Tongs Development
lenders.occupation: Lieutenant of the Tongs Development Organisation
lenders.loan_because:
The Tongs are a not-for-profit group of likeminded idiots, whose website has accidentally raised a substantial volume of money.

These funds are to be preserved to meet the future costs of the Tongs website; however, in the meantime we are eager to free them up for the benefit of entrepreneurs in the emerging markets. Thus, the Tongs Development Organisation was founded in 2010 to reinvest our wealth. Our investment in Kiva will be one strand in the rich tapestry that is our munificence.

The Tongs are particularly interested in supporting noodle stands and likeminded ventures.
lenders.occupational_info: We are eager to assist entrepreneurs with a human interest angle to their story. In particular, anyone with a noodle stand will receive our support (funds permiting).
